modules.description: This module samples 2D parametric curves using `Gg.p2` points, offering adaptive and uniform sampling strategies. It supports operations to construct samplings from functions, paths, or sequences, and to convert samplings to lists or sequences with optional cuts. Concrete use cases include rendering smooth curves in graphics applications and discretizing mathematical functions for numerical analysis.
